cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

The paper proposes a new loss function for deep metric learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method is evaluated on image datasets (cs.CV) and involves training a neural network for a classification task (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of the proposed method for clustering (cs.CL) and image retrieval (cs.MM).
